          .team-member-text
            %h4.team-member-name Lenny Turetsky
            .team-member-position CEO &amp; Founder
            %p.team-member-description Lenny Turetsky has spent 15 years in tech both as a senior developer at companies like SalesForce and Pivotal Labs and also as an entrepreneur. He has taught English in Korea and earned a CS degree from Yale University. He lives in San Francisco with his son Ezra and dog, Luigi.
      .col-lg-3.col-lg-offset-2.col-md-4.col-sm-6{"data-animation" => "fadeIn"}
