          .team-member-text
            %h4.team-member-name Fred Schoeneman
            .team-member-position CTO &amp; Co-Founder
            %p.team-member-description Fred Schoeneman is a former developer at GoPro and now consults with startups. He is a former Army infantryman, commercial diver, and a dropout from Stanford University. He splits his time between Oakland, Mendocino County, and Lake Tahoe, where he skis as much as he can.
